## Calendar Usage

### Appointment Date Selection
```tsx
<Calendar
  mode="single"
  selected={selectedDate}
  onSelect={setSelectedDate}
  disabled={(date) => 
    date < new Date() || 
    date.getDay() === 0 ||
    date.getDay() === 6
  }
  modifiers={{
    available: availableDates,
    busy: busyDates
  }}
  modifiersClassNames={{
    available: 'bg-green-50 text-green-800',
    busy: 'bg-gray-100 text-gray-400'
  }}
/>
```

toast.usage:
## Toast Usage

### Success Toast
```tsx
toast({
  title: "Appointment Confirmed",
  description: "Your appointment has been scheduled for January 15 at 2:00 PM.",
  variant: "success",
});
```

### Error Toast
```tsx
toast({
  title: "Unable to Schedule",
  description: "This time slot is no longer available. Please select another time.",
  variant: "destructive",
});
```

### With Action
```tsx
toast({
  title: "Message Sent",
  description: "Your message has been sent to Dr. Smith.",
  action: (
    <ToastAction altText="View message">View</ToastAction>
  ),
});
```

